  use wvdial. Thanks to: Björn Michaelsen <bmichaelsen@t-email.de> in bug #27506

  21 Aug 2003; Will Woods <wwoods@gentoo.org> wvdial-1.53-r1.ebuild:
  Marked stable for alpha

